# Project V1 Map

## Overview
This document summarizes the updates applied in this iteration and highlights remaining gaps.

## Implemented Updates
- Added balance and transaction domain models (`Balance`, `Transaction`) and a `Video` model to track uploads and points.
- Created a `BalanceController` for client/creator balance screens and add/withdraw actions.
- Created a `VideoController` to award points on upload and list creator video points.
- Expanded `AdminController` to show balance/points stats and configure point settings.
- Added new balance and points dashboards:
  - `client-balance.blade.php`
  - `creator-balance.blade.php`
  - `creator-video-points.blade.php`
  - `admin-video-points.blade.php`
- Added Laravel Mix setup (`package.json`, `webpack.mix.js`) and wired `mix()` assets in the layout.
- Introduced global dashboard styling via `resources/css/app.css` and `resources/js/app.js`.

## Project Structure Map
- `app/Http/Controllers`
  - `Admin/AdminController.php`: Admin dashboard + video points settings.
  - `Dashboard/BalanceController.php`: Balance views + add/withdraw actions.
  - `Dashboard/ClientController.php`: Client dashboard overview.
  - `Dashboard/CreatorController.php`: Creator dashboard + offer/support/order status.
  - `Dashboard/VideoController.php`: Creator video uploads + points totals.
