## Missing / To Be Implemented
- Database migrations for `balances`, `transactions`, and `videos`.
- Integration with Laravel Cashier (no dependency configured yet).
- Payment gateway integration (Stripe/PayPal) and secure OTP/email confirmation on balance operations.
- Real-time reporting for performance stats, campaigns, and invoice data.
- API endpoints for real-time balances/points updates.
- Admin CRUD screens for plan management if not already present.
- Production build pipeline for Laravel Mix (CI/CD step).

## Notes
- Current points and balance logic is implemented at controller level for the UI flow; once migrations and Cashier are added, logic should be updated to persist and validate properly.
- The layout now uses `mix()` helper; ensure `npm install && npm run dev` produces updated assets before deployment.
